law.history: Repealed 2008 Ky. Acts ch. 83, sec. 12, effective July 15, 2008. -- Amended 2007 Ky. Acts ch. 81, sec. 1, effective June 26, 2007. -- Amended 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 188, sec. 282, effective July 15, 1980. -- Amended 1968 Ky. Acts ch. 152, sec. 152. -- Created 1956 Ky. Acts ch. 131, sec. 1, effective May 18, 1956.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Register containing name of person from whom copper metal, copper wire, or copper cable is purchased required of dealers, vendors, and collectors of junk, metals, and used articles -- Contents of register -- Inspection of register -- Reports to sheriff and police department.
